6.title: Carl Fogarty
6.plot: Brian McFadden presents the dining challenge show in which contestants are invited to dinner at a mystery celebrity's house and must guess who their host is. Superbike champion Carl Fogarty plays host. Can the King of the Jungle avoid the dishes with his cryptic clues as to his identity or will his four diners bag the cash prize and hand him the rubber gloves?

7.title: Danielle Lloyd

Today, former Miss England and WAG Danielle Lloyd puts on a dinner party at her palatial home as she plays mystery host to four strangers. Will they score big and bag the winnings or will they get a yellow card after failing to guess her identity?

imdb.title: Who's Doing the Dishes?
plot: Over the course of a week, five different celebrities cook a meal for a group of four strangers, who must figure out the identity of each celebrity in order to win cash prizes.
